<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 18:10:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列交战，第 287 天：胡塞武装无人机杀死以色列人；国际法院对以色列占领作出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-287-houthi-drone-kills-israeli-icj-rules-on-israeli-occupation/00000190-cbe0-d5cb-a59c-efef02b40000</link><description>胡塞武装无人机袭击在特拉维夫造成以色列平民死亡、八人受伤 ■ 国际法院：以色列对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领是“事实上的吞并”，以色列定居点违反国际法 ■ 以色列国防军：越来越多的迹象表明哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·戴夫在上周的空袭中丧生 ■ 战争进入 287 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-287-houthi-drone-kills-israeli-icj-rules-on-israeli-occupation/00000190-cbe0-d5cb-a59c-efef02b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人对国际法院的“反犹太主义”裁决感到愤怒，巴勒斯坦总统表示正义已经胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-leaders-seethe-at-antisemitic-icj-palestinian-president-says-justice-has-won/00000190-cb67-decf-a7b2-dff7f2240000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：犹太人“不占领自己的土地” ■ 拉皮德：裁决“受到反犹太主义的玷污”，只为“伊斯兰恐怖主义”服务 ■ 本·格维尔、斯莫特里奇：吞并约旦河西岸的时间到了 ■ 蒂比：国际法院“准确地捕捉到了现实” ” ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯：“正义的胜利”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-leaders-seethe-at-antisemitic-icj-palestinian-president-says-justice-has-won/00000190-cb67-decf-a7b2-dff7f2240000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院称以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土“非法”，必须停止存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/world-court-israeli-occupation-of-palestinian-territories-unlawful-must-end-presence/00000190-cb67-dbb4-a7d2-db6fabec0000</link><description>世界法院称以色列一直实行种族隔离，应就其对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领做出赔偿</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/world-court-israeli-occupation-of-palestinian-territories-unlawful-must-end-presence/00000190-cb67-dbb4-a7d2-db6fabec0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土“非法”，必须停止存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-of-west-bank-east-jerusalem/00000190-cade-dfb6-afbe-effe53000000</link><description>尽管联合国最高法院的咨询意见不具有约束力，但针对以色列的裁决可能会导致国际社会对定居点运动实施更严厉的制裁</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 12:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-of-west-bank-east-jerusalem/00000190-cade-dfb6-afbe-effe53000000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列幸福指数排名高是一个弥天大谎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-israels-high-ranking-on-the-happiness-index-is-one-big-lie/00000190-c93b-dfb6-afbe-ef7baaca0000</link><description>以色列在国际幸福指数中的高排名掩盖了一个正在遭受希望丧失和冷漠的社会。要改变这种情况，我们必须培养一种不同的感觉：愤怒</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-israels-high-ranking-on-the-happiness-index-is-one-big-lie/00000190-c93b-dfb6-afbe-ef7baaca0000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装无人机对特拉维夫的致命袭击标志着自 10 月 7 日以来战争进入戏剧性的新阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/houthi-drone-strike-on-tel-aviv-marks-a-new-phase-in-the-october-7-war/00000190-ca69-db81-a3f7-fafd3dbf0000</link><description>胡塞武装装备了伊朗提供的日益先进的远程武器，他们表示特拉维夫现在将成为主要目标。这意味着以色列的多线战争变得更加激烈，而且冲突将演变成区域性的</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/houthi-drone-strike-on-tel-aviv-marks-a-new-phase-in-the-october-7-war/00000190-ca69-db81-a3f7-fafd3dbf0000</guid></item><item><title>网络中断导致航班停飞，给以色列和世界各地造成干扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-health-ministry-says-global-outage-causing-hospital-services-to-malfunction/00000190-c9cf-d3e0-a5fd-ebffe5480000</link><description>以色列卫生部报告称，该国 15 家医院关闭，造成严重混乱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-health-ministry-says-global-outage-causing-hospital-services-to-malfunction/00000190-c9cf-d3e0-a5fd-ebffe5480000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫无人机袭击造成 1 人死亡、8 人受伤；胡塞武装宣称对此事负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-eight-wounded-in-drone-attack-on-tel-aviv-houthis-claim-responsibility/00000190-c991-d3e0-a5fd-ebb55bbe0000</link><description>无人机爆炸造成八人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它识别出了这架无人机，但由于人为错误，没有拦截或激活警报器</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:52:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-eight-wounded-in-drone-attack-on-tel-aviv-houthis-claim-responsibility/00000190-c991-d3e0-a5fd-ebb55bbe0000</guid></item><item><title>“就连我当地的犹太社区现在也不支持以色列了。很难消化’</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-19/ty-article/.highlight/even-my-local-jewish-community-doesnt-stand-with-israel-now-its-hard-to-digest/00000190-c91b-d3e0-a5fd-ebbffe310000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名犹太裔美国人在经历加沙战争后的反犹太复国主义和反犹太主义后考虑搬到以色列，而一名以色列医生则搬到荷兰，以便她可以行医并过上自己的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-19/ty-article/.highlight/even-my-local-jewish-community-doesnt-stand-with-israel-now-its-hard-to-digest/00000190-c91b-d3e0-a5fd-ebbffe310000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普发誓要“结束因袭击以色列而引发的战争”，并将10月7日的责任归咎于拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/trump-vows-to-end-the-war-caused-by-the-attack-on-israel-blames-biden-for-october-7/00000190-c905-d258-a3ff-ed8d5a7f0001</link><description>前总统在接受共和党总统提名时承诺“结束本届政府制造的每一次国际危机”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/trump-vows-to-end-the-war-caused-by-the-attack-on-israel-blames-biden-for-october-7/00000190-c905-d258-a3ff-ed8d5a7f0001</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙停火条件成熟，内塔尼亚胡独自留在以色列的拒绝主义阵线上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-left-alone-on-israels-rejectionist-front-as-conditions-ripen-for-gaza-ceasefire/00000190-c748-db81-a3f7-f7dcc5610000</link><description>即使在政府内部，对人质协议的支持也越来越多，但泄密事件 - 以及总理本人 - 正在阻碍进展</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:02:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-left-alone-on-israels-rejectionist-front-as-conditions-ripen-for-gaza-ceasefire/00000190-c748-db81-a3f7-f7dcc5610000</guid></item><item><title>一场“历史性”的美国访问正在等待，但内塔尼亚胡将从拜登和特朗普那里听到同样的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-u-s-viawaits-but-netanyahu-will-hear-the-same-message-from-biden-trump/00000190-c765-dbfd-a594-c767a96e0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚以色列总理是否会与拜登（他认为拜登是跛脚鸭）或特朗普会面，但他们都会告诉他“克服它”并结束战争。 最广泛认同的观点是内塔尼亚胡将最终批准了一项人质交易，可能是结束他的犯罪噩梦的认罪协议的一部分 ■ 比比终于面临他的滑铁卢——好吧，不是真的</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-u-s-viawaits-but-netanyahu-will-hear-the-same-message-from-biden-trump/00000190-c765-dbfd-a594-c767a96e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡访问华盛顿将再次引发人质家属之间的分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/in-washington-visit-netanyahu-will-once-again-spark-division-among-hostages-families/00000190-c748-d258-a3ff-e7c9be560000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡将与被扣押在加沙的以色列人质的一些亲属一起进入国会，他们希望利用这个机会倡导达成协议。其他人会在外面抗议，指责总理阻碍谈判并利用他们的困境来实现他的个人目标</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/in-washington-visit-netanyahu-will-once-again-spark-division-among-hostages-families/00000190-c748-d258-a3ff-e7c9be560000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：以色列和哈马斯在“目标线”附近停火，最终问题正在谈判中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/idf-says-checking-possible-drone-attack-after-several-injured-in-tel-aviv-blast/00000190-c8c3-dfb6-afbe-efe376560000</link><description>国际法院称以色列对巴勒斯坦领土的占领“非法”，必须结束 ■ 以色列定居者在约旦河西岸哈瓦拉射杀一名巴勒斯坦人，冲突爆发 ■ 以色列国防军表示，自早上以来，黎巴嫩向以色列发射了 65 枚火箭弹和无人机 ■ 德国外长呼吁加沙停火，称以色列国防军“一次又一次”袭击安全区 ■ 胡塞武装声称对特拉维夫无人机袭击负责，造成一名以色列人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，越来越多的证据表明哈马斯的德伊夫在以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 计算机系统导致以色列医院中断</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:24:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-live/idf-says-checking-possible-drone-attack-after-several-injured-in-tel-aviv-blast/00000190-c8c3-dfb6-afbe-efe376560000</guid></item><item><title>当一名极端正统派定居者提出向一名极端世俗的特拉维夫人传授犹太教时，发生了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</link><description>有一天，有人敲我的门。那是一个极端正统派的人，微笑着问我是否想学习犹太教。我邀请他进来</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-an-haredi-settler-offered-to-teach-an-ultra-secular-tel-avivian-about-judaism/00000190-c7d8-dfb6-afbe-effaf8a20000</guid></item><item><title>迈克·约翰逊威胁要逮捕扰乱内塔尼亚胡国会演讲的议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</link><description>在共和党大会间隙的“向亲以色列民选官员致敬”上，约翰逊议长告诉共和党犹太人：我们是唯一亲以色列的政党</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/this-is-an-attack-on-americans-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-appeal-to-republicans/00000190-c7d0-dbfd-a594-c7f76fbf0001</guid></item><item><title>在 10 月 7 日之后的世界中，犹太人不再有应许之地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</link><description>去年对犹太人来说是非常不安的一年，他们感觉一段独特的宽容和安全时期可能已经结束。这不仅是哈马斯的袭击，也是以色列内部政治的事态发展</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-the-post-october-7-world-there-are-no-promised-lands-for-jews/00000190-c6aa-d3e0-a5fd-efbf138a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端主义政府煽动对人质的仇恨，并产生了后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</link><description>一小部分但直言不讳的以色列选民在极端主义领导人的鼓励下，猛烈抨击人质亲属在试图确保加沙被囚禁的亲人获释时所做的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:55:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-extremist-government-is-stoking-hate-against-hostages-and-there-are-consequences/00000190-c67d-de8b-adfc-df7da0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列实施武器禁运？承认巴勒斯坦吗？英国新政府即将做出的政策决定承诺“为善的力量”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</link><description>包括外交大臣大卫·拉米在内的新英国工党政府无意卷入有关以色列和加沙的两极分化和政治有毒的政策辩论，而是更愿意在制裁暴力的约旦河西岸定居者等问题上保持共识。但正如一位专家指出的那样：“你永远无法逃避以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/arms-embargo-on-israel-recognize-palestine-looming-policy-decisions-for-new-u-k-govt/00000190-c65a-dbfd-a594-c67fd2860000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院将裁定以色列占领约旦河西岸是否非法：为什么是现在以及以色列和巴勒斯坦人将如何反应？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</link><description>海牙最新的历史性判决：国际法院的程序与国际刑事法院有何不同？ ■ 以色列是否配合听证会？ ■ 如果法院裁定以色列对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领非法，会产生什么影响？</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-rule-on-legality-of-israels-occupation-why-now-and-what-will-be-the-reactions/00000190-c5ba-dbfd-a594-c5bfc8e70000</guid></item></channel></rss>